const palette = {
    charcoal1: "rgba(58, 58, 58, 1.0)",
    charcoal1Transparent: "rgba(58, 58, 58, 0.4)",
    charcoal2: "#dcdcdc",
    charcoal3: "rgba(133, 133, 133, 1.0)",

    blue1: "rgba(95, 185, 243, 1.0)",
    blue1Transparent: "rgba(95, 185, 243, 0.4)",

    teal1: "rgba(14, 181, 236, 1.0)",
    teal1Transparent: "rgba(14, 181, 236, 0.4)",

    gold1: "rgba(182, 176, 94, 1.0)",
    gold1Transparent: "rgba(182, 176, 94, 0.4)",

    black1: "rgba(0, 0, 0, 1.0)",
    black1Transparent: "rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.6)",

    white1: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 1)",
    white1Transparent: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8)",

    transparent: "rgba(255, 255, 255, 0)"
}

export default palette;
